  "detailed_description": "Player will act as a bear who master in Chinese blade. He travels around the world and challenging Kungfu masters from various countries:<br>the guardian warrior at the Inari Shrine, the skeleton king in the dark dungeon and the pirate captain from the Caribbean sea....<br>We even adapted different music styles for each themed level: traditional Japanese sounds, Shamisen music, Lo-Fi, HipHop, Trap, and Reggae!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=474 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristic</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Listening to the music rhythm and fight against opponents.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Different enemies feature in various attack styles. Players can identify the attack direction and beat back accordingly.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>During the music highlight, players can use combo hit unlimitedly.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
